====================================================================================================
1.1.0
====================================================================================================

* Adding comprehensive recordings
  - add functionality for comprehensive cohort recordings to be loaded from disk
  - add new recording table
  - recordings are stored on disk according to visit, participant UID, and cognitive variable
    name as stored and identified in Opal (eg., 001/A123456/COG_ALPTME_REC2_COM.wav )

* Workflow improvements
  - implement new deferral process using expanded deferred states: NULL, requested, pending, 
    resolved
  - a typist requests a deferral setting the deferred status of a test to "requested"
  - administrators review and change the deferred status of a test in the test_entry view to "pending"
  - a test's deferred status changes to "resolved" after the first typist edit that completes the test
  - participant allocation is restricted on a complete by complete assigment basis by checking
    during assignment request if there is a sibling assignment, and if so, that the sibling 
    assignment has all tests completed

====================================================================================================
1.0.2
====================================================================================================

* Adding assignment reassign
  - link the cenozo site and cedar assignment db tables to track
    which site the assignment is currently assigned to
  - add functionality to automatically identify 2 typists with no language restriction
    for reassigning deferred bilingual content to
  - add reassign operation

* Adding dictionary word transfer
  - add operations for tranferring words among dictionaries associated with a test
    including transferring to the 'null' dictionary (ie., trash)
  - primary dictionary words are prohibited from transfers
  - add operations for dictionary transfer_word

* Adding intrusion deletion for ranked_word tests
  - add a delete button beside REY test intrusion entries so that typists
    can remove accidentally added intrusion fields
  - add operation to delete a test_entry_ranked_word entry

* Transcription UI improvements
  - add javascript mouseover and mouseout functions to highlight rows in REY test
    transcription table

* Adjudication and Transcription UI improvements
  - add javascript mouseover andmouseout functions to highlight rows in UI tables
  - clean up interface appearance
  - fix buggy use of empty/intrusion text input fields
  - load english and french words when adjudicating or transcribing bilingual data

* Adding supervisor role
  - add the supervisor role for working with adjudications, reports, tests (list, view),
    notes, users (list)

* Remove deferral process
  - removed the deferall process when a typist selects audio_status={unavailable}

* Adding new "collection" feature
  - collections are arbitrary groups of participant
  - can be locked so that editing is restricted to a list of specified users only
  - restrict select reports by collection remains to be implemented

* Adding assignment delete
  - add assignment delete operation
  - allow administrators to delete open assignments
  - assignments cannot be deleted if
    1) their end_datetime is not null (ie., "closed")
    2) the last edit activity is within a set retention time (eg., 8 hours)

====================================================================================================
1.0.1
====================================================================================================

* Incorporate cenozo language restrictions
  - add operations to edit, list, view languages
  - add operations to add, edit, delete a user's language restrictions
  - revamp how ranked word sets are implemented by adding ranked_word_set_has_language table
  - remove defunct word_*_id columns from the ranked_word_set table
  - add language_id column to word table

* Performance improvements to word count views
  - changed the way dictionary views make use of word counts so that the db views
    could be implmented in sql with fewer joins

* Dropped defunct recording table

====================================================================================================
1.0.0
====================================================================================================

* Adding management of a service's jurisdiction and region-site associations
  - adminstrators can now add/edit/delete which sites a region is assigned to
  - incorporated from cenozo

* Adding audio and participant enumerated status
  - audio status refined to unusable, salvageable and unavailable states
  - participant status includes refusals and interviewer prompting during FAS and AFT tests

* Event system now tracks when participants are released to services

====================================================================================================
0.1.3
====================================================================================================

* Adding typist breaks
  - added functionality for typists to take timed breaks and for administrators to
  manage them
  - added away_time and user_time tables (copied and adapted from sabretooth)

* Improved performance and functionality of assignment list
  - created views of test_entry adjudicate/deferred/completed counts to allow
  sorting assignments
  - assignment list can be restricted to open, closed or unrestricted

* Adding start and end datetimes to assignment table
  - track the datetime when assignments are first created until they are finished with or
  without adjudication

* Adding enhanced word management
  - added mispelled words column to test table
  - created views of word usage counts based on test type
  - words having zero usage count can be identified and deleted
  - typists are notified of and prevented submission of known mispelled words
  - words can be moved among dictionaries of the same test type

* Adding reports
  - added typist productivity and assignment status reports

* Enhanced test adjudication management
  - created an assignment manager in the business layer
  - adjudication test_entry is created and updated during the adjudication process at the
  daughter table level
  - changed test_entry adjudicate column to default to NULL to accomodate tertiary status:
  NULL (never adjudicated), 0 (adjudicated), 1 (requiring adjudication)

* Improved perfomance during assignment creation
  - created a view of sabretooth's recording table

* Simplified handling of word candidates during transcription and adjudication
  - removed word_candidate columns from ranked word, classification and alpha numeric tests
  - added ranked_word_set_id column to test_entry_ranked_word

====================================================================================================
0.1.2
====================================================================================================

* Adding unique constraint to assignment table
  - assignments are unique to participant and user

* Adding word classifications
  - word entries are classified and colored at the UI layer: primary (no coloring),
  candidate (yellow), intrusion (red), variant (blue)

* Adding text autocompletion
  - added jquery autocompletion for text input fields
  - added word list pull operation to retrieve a dictionary's words for populating the
  autocomplete widget

* Adding unique constraint to alpha numeric and classification test entry type tables
  - entries are unique on test_entry_id and rank columns

* Adding notes to test_entry
  - created test_entry_note table so that users and administrators can pass notes
  particular to a given test_entry
  - removed defunct note column from test_entry table

* Adding entry field additions
  - created add button to append new text input fields to the UI for alpha numeric
  test transcriptions

====================================================================================================
0.1.1
====================================================================================================

* Adding new operations to roles
  - added push new test_entry daughter table entries as part of the
  adjudication and transcription process
